description.narrative:
Project outputs: 
These activities will result in the following:
25 local trainers trained by a regional expert;
105 youth take part in entrepreneurship and management trainings, including enterprises;
30 business plans submitted, 10 business plans approved by the jury;
50 students take part in CV, motivation letter and job interview training;
5 businesses receive loans from finance institution; 
5 businesses promoted nationally and internationally; 
5 BSCK staff receive training.

Project outcomes:
20 local trainers ready to deliver entrepreneurship and management trainings;
10 SMEs started or grown;
75% survival rate of businesses 3 years after launch;
10 students to take part in interviews with employers 
20 jobs created by supported businesses;
5 successful matchmaking with investors;
5 BSCK staff capacity developed.
